metadata.description: burst_ HAHAkid drawings - artwork 01 / Pepe Frog Laughs: HAHAHAHAHAHAHAH Pepe Frog Laughs - This drawing is by "H&ART BLOCK"s aka @bullishseller ´s kid. He sent it to me and wrote quote: "My kid thinks frogs are funny i guess" and I had to create an AR animation for his kid to enjoy.. because HAHA is the future.. every kid knows it and is intuitively guided by the force and love of creativity, spontaneity and pure joy of HAHA.. let this be a reminder that everyone can be immersed in that state of mind. - Sound Design by: burst - Hco (Peru) March 2023, 31 sec, MP4, 2160 × 3200
